    <h3><a href="#" data-metrics="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;Toggle Footer Dropdown&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;Foreign Dispatch Podcastt&quot;}">Foreign Dispatch Podcast</a></h3>
    <div class="promo-bucket" data-metrics-all="" data-metrics="{&quot;action&quot;:&quot;Click Footer Promo&quot;}" style="overflow: visible;">
        <a href="http://www.npr.org/rss/podcast/podcast_detail.php?siteId=6661111"><img src="http://media.npr.org/images/podcasts/img90/npr_foreigndispatch_90.jpg" alt="Health Podcast" class="pod" height="60" width="60"></a>
        <div class="bucketblock" style="overflow: visible;">
            <p>A weekly podcast of the biggest news and best stories from NPR's foreign correspondents from around the world.</p>
